{"tid":1232772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個遊行睇清哂香港人","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:27:19.000Z","uid":3390,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e369ae19f183091b2077efa511696776967c96ee","tid":1232772,"uid":3390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"一直以來連登都有人開post分化大家<br />\n港女 大陸妹<br />\n公屋 私樓<br />\n廢老 年輕人<br />\n<br />\n又不斷踩香港 開移民post 罵香港人冇人情味 冇同情心 自私自利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今次遊行睇到既並唔係平時網上所講野既 <br />\n大家目標一樣 一齊努力 鼓勵 同巴士拍手 大家一齊歡呼 讓救護車 睇到出並唔係見錢開眼 見利忘義既人<br />\n<br />\n雖然仲沒達到目標 但我希望大家唔好再比網上既評市洗腦 其實香港仲係一個好撚正 好撚有人情味既地方 成日講走走走 不如一齊諗方法搞好佢啦 ！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">  屌 我真係好撚鐘意香港呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"63074a45c14b5a5ed5606d6e6747b04f012e5b1f","tid":1232772,"uid":3390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"講到眼濕濕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f9e5aa8258651b103436853b58ffce29539b0c","tid":1232772,"uid":194358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"寧做自由閪，不做政權龜"},{"pid":"62529967044ba1c5c72cd953fc163f0b30f61a95","tid":1232772,"uid":3390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"United We Stand <br />\nDivided We Fall<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}